# ACOB CRM3 вЂ” Full Platform Replication

Build a complete CRM platform that replicates every feature of the third-party Meter System at `http://8.208.16.168:9310`. The new platform will use the existing API as its data source, giving ACOB full control of their data, UI, and user experience.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Architecture Decision: Vite + React + TypeScript with a Node.js/Express backend proxy.**
> The backend acts as a proxy to the third-party API (`8.208.16.168:9310`), so credentials and the upstream URL are never exposed to the browser. All data flows through our backend.

> [!WARNING]
> **This is a large project (~20+ pages, 144 API endpoints).** The plan below covers the complete replication. We will build it phase by phase, with the first deliverable being a working dashboard + navigation + auth flow.

> [!CAUTION]
> **No secrets will be hardcoded.** The upstream API URL and credentials will be stored in `.env` files only.

---

## Reference Platform Analysis

### Sidebar Navigation (7 sections, 20+ pages)

| Section | Sub-pages |
|---------|-----------|
| **Dashboard** | Main dashboard with 4 stat cards + 4 charts |
| **Token Generate** | Credit Token, Clear Tamper Token, Clear Credit Token, Set Maximum Power Limit Token |
| **Token Record** | Credit Token Record, Clear Tamper Record, Clear Credit Record, Set Max Power Limit Record |
| **Remote Operation** | Meter Reading, Meter Control, Meter Token |
| **Remote Operation Task** | Meter Reading Task, Meter Control Task, Meter Token Task |
| **Data Report** | Long Nonpurchase Situation, Low Purchase Situation, Consumption Statistics, Interval Data |
| **Management** | Customer, Account, Tariff, Gateway |

### Dashboard Charts
1. **Purchase Money** вЂ” Bar chart over date axis
2. **Hourly Success Rate** вЂ” Line chart over 24h axis
3. **Abnormal Alarm** вЂ” Pie chart (No Data Report, Current Unbalance, Current Reverse, Cover Open, Terminal Cover Open, Magnetic Interference, Battery Low, Relay Open)
4. **Daily Consumption** вЂ” Bar chart with Daily/Monthly toggle

### API Endpoints (144 total, 26 groups)
All endpoints are `POST` with JSON body, returning `{ code, reason, result }` envelope. Key groups: Account, Customer, DailyData, DailyDataMeter, Dashboard, Debt, DLMS, DLT645, DLT645Task, EventNotification, File, Gateway, GPRSMeterTask, GPRSOnlineStatus, Item, LoadProfile, Log, Meter, PrepayReport, RemoteMeterTask, Role, Station, Tariff, Token, UpdateFirmwareTask, User.

