### [Backend] Core Setup

#### [NEW] [index.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACOB/Desktop/VS%20Code/acob-crm3/backend/src/index.ts)
- Express server with CORS, JSON body parser, cookie-parser
- Mounts all API route groups
- Proxies all `/api/*` requests to upstream `8.208.16.168:9310`
- Stores auth token in HTTP-only cookie

#### [NEW] [upstream.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACOB/Desktop/VS%20Code/acob-crm3/backend/src/services/upstream.ts)
- Axios instance configured with upstream base URL from `.env`
- Intercepts responses to unwrap `{ code, reason, result }` envelope
- Forwards auth token from cookies

#### [NEW] [proxy.ts](file:///c:/Users/ACOB/Desktop/VS%20Code/acob-crm3/backend/src/api/proxy.ts)
- Generic proxy that forwards any `/api/*` POST to upstream
- Used for all 144 endpoints вЂ” no need for individual route files initially
- Adds auth token header from session

