## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. **TypeScript Build Check** вЂ” Run `npx tsc --noEmit` in both `frontend/` and `backend/` to verify type consistency
   ```
   cd c:\Users\ACOB\Desktop\VS Code\acob-crm3\frontend && npx tsc --noEmit
   cd c:\Users\ACOB\Desktop\VS Code\acob-crm3\backend && npx tsc --noEmit
   ```

2. **Dev Server Startup** вЂ” Verify both servers start without errors
   ```
   cd c:\Users\ACOB\Desktop\VS Code\acob-crm3\backend && npm run dev
   cd c:\Users\ACOB\Desktop\VS Code\acob-crm3\frontend && npm run dev
   ```

### Browser Verification
3. **Login Flow** вЂ” Navigate to the app, log in with admin/ACOB_admin, verify dashboard loads
4. **Dashboard Data** вЂ” Verify all 4 stat cards show real numbers, all 4 charts render with data
5. **Page Navigation** вЂ” Click through every sidebar item, verify each page loads and shows data
6. **CRUD Operations** вЂ” Test Add/Edit/Delete on Customer and Account management pages
7. **Token Generation** вЂ” Test Recharge flow on Credit Token page

### Cross-Reference
8. **Side-by-side comparison** вЂ” Open both the reference platform and our app, compare each page visually to confirm data and layout parity
